# Secrets (root-level only — charts/*/templates/secrets/ are Helm
# templates, not actual secrets). Use `/secrets/*` (not `/secrets/`)
# so the negation below works: gitignore docs say a re-included file
# is impossible if the parent directory itself is excluded, only if
# its CONTENTS are excluded with a glob.
/secrets/*
# DO commit `.example` template files so operators have a starting
# shape for the gitignored .txt files (ADR-048 PR-B2 added Docker Hub
# PAT templates).
!/secrets/*.example
*.pem
*.key
# Chart-vendored public trust roots are explicit exceptions —
# these are public CA certificates (no private key material).
# Backlog #13 anchor: SwissSign 2020-2 root extracted from
# `main_signed.pdf` PAdES chain.
!charts/audittrace/trust-store/static-roots/*.pem
!charts/audittrace/trust-store/static-roots/*.crt

# Docker
docker-compose.override.yml

